milestones.description: Clive Lloyd has become the top scorer for WI in ODIs with 361 runs, going past Viv Richards's 328
Julien has become the top wicket-taker for WI in ODIs with 18 wickets, going past Andy Roberts's 17
This is the lowest match aggregate (358) involving teams West Indies & Pakistan in ODIs
Fredericks has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (12) for WI, going past Holder
Majid Khan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for PAK, going past Asif Masood
Asif Iqbal and Javed Miandad's 37-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between Wasim Raja and Javed Miandad
Asif Iqbal and Imran Khan's 67-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 12 between Pervez Mir and Javed Miandad
